{"tid":1375813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩食飯聽到幾個老人家講野 真係眼濕濕","createTime":"2019-07-28T07:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T12:55:53.000Z","uid":16214,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"29380a34694ee27fef9db66031a4dd856d4c037a","tid":1375813,"uid":16214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:01:32.000Z","msg":"岩岩我食飯既時候<br />\n實在太多人 所以要搭枱<br />\n咁我就被分配到一位老人家身旁<br />\n一開始我都覺得佢係深藍廢老個類<br />\n但好對唔住 係我以貌取人<br />\n佢臨走唔知佢聽到佢隔離講啲乜<br />\n就覆左佢一句 <br />\n如果依個政府無問題 就唔會咁多人出黎<br />\n佢隔離個位就拍手 大聲話講得好<br />\n之後佢隔離個位就話<br />\n如果覺得我有罪我有問題既話<br />\n你大可以捉我番去審 <br />\n未審即無罪 你要拉要鎖我無所謂<br />\n但你下下都打到班後生半死<br />\n就押人上車<br />\n每次都話係用最低武力 <br />\n但下下都用棍扑人個頭 下下都係圍毆<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁樣唔係警察所為</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n聽完老實講 我老人老狗都眼濕濕<br />\n係我錯以貌取人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860c395a8d6ba67c14deaf3b7e60116b9d6a63dc","tid":1375813,"uid":211466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:04:32.000Z","msg":"智慧老人"},{"pid":"6b69f5b3c1a67cfcbc73e488f51277edefc96f89","tid":1375813,"uid":16214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"860c395a8d6ba67c14deaf3b7e60116b9d6a63dc","tid":1375813,"uid":211466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:04:32.000Z","msg":"智慧老人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T07:11:04.000Z","msg":"個一刻我真係好希望佢地係我屋企人<br />\n就連當我726話要去機場靜坐<br />\n我屋企人都淨係識話我去黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e6e2ae7ab2e40a0c78c2f35397674ac4b412b3","tid":1375813,"uid":211466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6b69f5b3c1a67cfcbc73e488f51277edefc96f89","tid":1375813,"uid":16214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"860c395a8d6ba67c14deaf3b7e60116b9d6a63dc","tid":1375813,"uid":211